what is schema

mongoose schema help defines the structure of the document, default values, validators,etc

we can define the struture 
we can set document filed data type

const playlistSchema=new mongoose.Schema({
name:string,
age:{
type:number,
require :true
}




})
in require mean it must the data type number


what is models






A mongoose model is a wrapper on the mongoose schema.
a mongoose model provides an interface to the data base for creating, quering,updating,deleteing record etc


notes model create mean collection create 
const Playlist=new mongoose.model("collectionName",define schema )

